snippet.title: Blood of Vladula jr. - trailer
snippet.description:
Blood of Vladula jr., a 2D platformer made for the Pico-8 fantasy system is available for free now at https://slumma.itch.io

Playable in browser, downloads available for Windows, Mac, Linux, Raspberry Pi, and as a Pico-8 cart.

The song in the trailer is a chiptune cover of Night of the Vampire by Roky Erickson
